<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <main class="page-shell narrow fade-in">
    <section class="glass-card rules-card">
      <p class="eyebrow danger-eyebrow">Danger Zone</p>
      <h1>RULES — READ CAREFULLY</h1>
      <p class="rules-subtitle">
        Breaking these rules will result in your submission being marked as cheated with a score of 0/20.
      </p>

      <% if (formError) { %>
        <p class="error-text rules-error" role="alert"><%= formError %></p>
      <% } %>

      <ol class="rules-list">
        <li>DO NOT switch tabs during the quiz. Even accidental tab switching will be detected and your quiz will be auto-submitted with a score of 0/20.</li>
        <li>DO NOT refresh the page during the quiz.</li>
        <li>DO NOT use external help, Google, friends, or any cheats.</li>
        <li>You have ONLY ONE attempt. Submissions are LOCKED FOREVER.</li>
        <li>Read each question carefully. You CANNOT go back to change answers after moving to the next question.</li>
        <li>Be honest. We track everything.</li>
        <li>Once you start the quiz, finish it in one sitting. Do not close the browser.</li>
      </ol>

      <form class="rules-form" action="/rules" method="POST">
        <label class="rules-checkbox">
          <input id="acceptRules" name="acceptRules" type="checkbox">
          <span>I have read and understood all the rules. I agree to follow them.</span>
        </label>
        <button id="rulesContinueBtn" class="btn btn-primary full-width" type="submit" disabled>I Agree, Continue</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      const checkbox = document.querySelector('#acceptRules');
      const button = document.querySelector('#rulesContinueBtn');

      if (!checkbox || !button) return;

      checkbox.addEventListener('change', () => {
        button.disabled = !checkbox.checked;
      });
    });
  </script>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
